  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will be an open label, single arm, phase I study intended to identify the safety
      and tolerability of &quot;AML Cell Vaccine&quot; given to eligible MDS RAEB-2 and AML patients who have
      achieved a best response of complete remission or partial remission following their first or
      second course of standard induction chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
